unk_9c63f9d.value:
OWC_SMP_CHECK()
-- wake up supporting monsters
for i, idMonster in pairs (idChanters) do
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idMonster) and Hydra.ActorIsAlive(idMonster) then
		Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idMonster, true)
		Hydra.ActorSetIdleAnim(idMonster, S_DEFAULT_IDLE)
	end
end

-- play empowered anim, then transform
if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idChanneler) and Hydra.ActorIsAlive(idChanneler) then
	-- transform
	Hydra.ActorSetInvulnerable(idSubject, false)
	Hydra.QActorStopAllQueuedActions(idSubject);
	Hydra.ActorTriggerPowerAtFeet(idSubject, S_GOATMAN_TRANSFORM);

	-- Wait for transform
	Hydra.Wait(1)

	-- wake up channeler and remove ropes
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idChanneler) and Hydra.ActorIsAlive(idChanneler) then
		Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idChanneler, true)
		Hydra.ActorSetIdleAnim(idChanneler, S_DEFAULT_IDLE)
		Hydra.ActorRemoveComplexEffect(idChanneler, ropesBySorcId[idChanneler])
	end	
else
	-- wake up subject
	Hydra.ActorSetInvulnerable(idSubject, false)
	Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idSubject, true)
	Hydra.ActorSetIdleAnim(idSubject, S_DEFAULT_IDLE)
end

unk_993f312.value:
idSubject = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idSelf, "SUBJECT")[1]
idChanters = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idSelf, "CHANTERS")
idChanneler = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idSelf, "CHANNELER")[1]
ropesBySorcId = {}

-- setup Subject
if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idSubject) and Hydra.ActorIsAlive(idSubject) then
	Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idSubject, false)
	Hydra.ActorSetInvulnerable(idSubject, true)
	Hydra.ActorSetIdleAnim(idSubject, S_GOATMAN_STUNNED)
end

-- setup Chanters
for i, idMonster in pairs (idChanters) do
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idMonster) and Hydra.ActorIsAlive(idMonster) then 
		Hydra.ActorSetIdleAnim(idMonster, S_GOATMAN_CHANT)
		Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idMonster, false)
	end
end

-- setup Channeler
if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idSubject) and Hydra.ActorIsAlive(idSubject) and Hydra.ActorIsValid(idChanneler) and Hydra.ActorIsAlive(idChanneler) then
	Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idChanneler, false)
	Hydra.ActorSetIdleAnim(idChanneler, S_GOATMAN_SORC_CHANNEL)
	rope = Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroupActorToActor(idChanneler, idSubject, S_ROPE_VFX, true)
	ropesBySorcId[idChanneler] = rope
end
